little zizou is an 2008 indian film in hindi , gujarati , and english , written and directed by sooni taraporevala .   little zizou is a fast-paced , exuberant , yet poignant comedy about how two battling mumbai families finally come to terms .   little zizou won the " rajat kamal " of ' national film award for best film on family welfare ' category at the 56th national film awards .